description:
Trained as a Roman soldier, Marcus Salvius was sent to serve in Britain, keeping order amongst people weary of the Roman yoke.
But Marcus knew he had British blood in his veins, and when oppression became harsher, his loyalty was tested beyond breaking point. He found himself an outlaw, leading an all-out rebellion against his former masters!
name: Outlaw!
